Description:
This item is being removed from the roadmap as it is no longer accurate. We apologize for any inconvenience. Integration of Universal Print with the Microsoft 365 Copilot phone app will enable users to add work/school printers to their phones. Once the printers are installed on the phone, the user can print to them from any phone app that has a print action.
GA date: March CY2026
Preview date: December CY2025
Title: Universal Print: Mobile print from the phone
